[[cdo:9 nguŏk 22 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:9 goe̍h 22 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:九月廿二]] {{Lunisolar September}} '''September 22''' is the 22nd day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft}} and its day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} {{ill|1189|ja|1189|12=draft}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|12=draft}} appointed {{ill|Kōzaisei Kiyoshige|ja|葛西清重|12=draft}} as the chief administrator (奥州総奉行), thereby consolidating control over Ōshu. * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} {{ill|1683|ja|1683|12=draft}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|12=draft}} ） – In Kyoto, the wife of the great Buddhist priest (大経師) – known as {{ill|O-san and Tedai Shigehei|ja|おさんと手代茂兵衛|12=draft}} – was executed for adultery. This incident provided material for works such as {{ill|Nishikaze’s|ja|西鶴|12=draft}} "Kōshoku Gonin Onna" and {{ill|Chikamatsu’s|ja|近松|12=draft}} "Daikyōshi Mukireki". * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|12=draft}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|12=draft}} ） – The lord of the Aizu domain, {{ill|Matsudaira Katamori|ja|松平容保|12=draft}} , opened his castle ({{Tsurugajo}} ) by "opening the castle" ceremony; Aizu later surrendered to the imperial forces.
== Births == * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} {{ill|1852|ja|1852|12=draft}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|12=draft}} ） – The future Emperor {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治天皇|12=draft}} , the 122nd emperor († {{ill|1912|ja|1912|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} {{ill|1311|ja|1311|12=draft}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Hojo Ujitoki|ja|北条師時|12=draft}} , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* {{ill|1275|ja|1275|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} {{ill|1773|ja|1773|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tanuma Yoshinori|ja|田沼意明|12=draft}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|12=draft}} ).
