== Deaths == * {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1311|ja|1311|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Hojo Ujitoki|ja|北条師時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* {{ill|1275|ja|1275|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1773|ja|1773|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tanuma Yoshinori|ja|田沼意明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
