* {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1773|ja|1773|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tanuma Yoshinori|ja|田沼意明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

