* {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1189|ja|1189|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  appointed {{ill|Kōzaisei Kiyoshige|ja|葛西清重|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  as the chief administrator (奥州総奉行), thereby consolidating control over Ōshu.
* {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1683|ja|1683|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – In Kyoto, the wife of the great Buddhist priest (大経師) – known as {{ill|O-san and Tedai Shigehei|ja|おさんと手代茂兵衛|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  – was executed for adultery. This incident provided material for works such as {{ill|Nishikaze’s|ja|西鶴|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  "Kōshoku Gonin Onna" and {{ill|Chikamatsu’s|ja|近松|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  "Daikyōshi Mukireki".
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The lord of the Aizu domain, {{ill|Matsudaira Katamori|ja|松平容保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , opened his castle ({{Tsurugajo}} ) by "opening the castle" ceremony; Aizu later surrendered to the imperial forces.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1852|ja|1852|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The future Emperor {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 122nd emperor († {{ill|1912|ja|1912|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1311|ja|1311|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Hojo Ujitoki|ja|北条師時|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* {{ill|1275|ja|1275|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1773|ja|1773|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tanuma Yoshinori|ja|田沼意明|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

