{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月廿二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 22일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 22''' is the 22nd day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1189|ja|1189|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} appointed {{ill|Kōzaisei Kiyoshige|ja|葛西清重|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} as the chief administrator (奥州総奉行), thereby consolidating control over Ōshu. * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1683|ja|1683|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – In Kyoto, the wife of the great Buddhist priest (大経師) – known as {{ill|O-san and Tedai Shigehei|ja|おさんと手代茂兵衛|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} – was executed for adultery. This incident provided material for works such as {{ill|Nishikaze’s|ja|西鶴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} "Kōshoku Gonin Onna" and {{ill|Chikamatsu’s|ja|近松|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} "Daikyōshi Mukireki". * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The lord of the Aizu domain, {{ill|Matsudaira Katamori|ja|松平容保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , opened his castle ({{Tsurugajo|qq=}} ) by "opening the castle" ceremony; Aizu later surrendered to the imperial forces.
== Births == * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1852|ja|1852|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The future Emperor {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 122nd emperor († {{ill|1912|ja|1912|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1311|ja|1311|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Hojo Ujitoki|ja|北条師時|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* {{ill|1275|ja|1275|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1773|ja|1773|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tanuma Yoshinori|ja|田沼意明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
