{{Not to be confused with|September 22|qq=September 22}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月廿二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 22일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 22''' is the 22nd day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}} . == Events == * [[:en:Bunji (era)|Bunji]] 5th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1189|1189]] [[:en:November 2|November 2]] ） – [[:en:Minamoto no Yoritomo|Minamoto no Yoritomo]] appointed {{ill|Kōzaisei Kiyoshige|ja|葛西清重|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōzaisei Kiyoshige|qq=}} as the chief administrator (奥州総奉行), thereby consolidating control over Ōshu. * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenwa (Japan)|qq=}} 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1683|ja|1683|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1683|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 10|November 10]] ） – In Kyoto, the wife of the great Buddhist priest (大経師) – known as {{ill|O-san and Tedai Shigehei|ja|おさんと手代茂兵衛|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/O-san and Tedai Shigehei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} – was executed for adultery. This incident provided material for works such as {{ill|Nishikaze’s|ja|西鶴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishikaze’s|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 井原西鶴}} "Kōshoku Gonin Onna" and {{ill|Chikamatsu’s|ja|近松|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chikamatsu’s|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近松門左衛門}} "Daikyōshi Mukireki". * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}} [[:en:November 6|November 6]] ） – The lord of the Aizu domain, [[:en:Matsudaira Katamori|Matsudaira Katamori]] , opened his castle ({{Tsurugajo|qq=}} ) by "opening the castle" ceremony; Aizu later surrendered to the imperial forces.
== Births == * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 5th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1852|ja|1852|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1852|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 3|November 3]] ） – The future Emperor [[:en:Emperor Meiji|Meiji]] , the 122nd emperor († {{ill|1912|ja|1912|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1912|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Ōchō|Ōchō]] 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1311|ja|1311|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1311|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 3|November 3]] ） – [[:en:Hōjō Morotoki|Hojo Ujitoki]] , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* [[:en:1275|1275]] ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/An'ei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安永 (元号)}} 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1773|ja|1773|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1773|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 22|October 22]] ） – {{ill|Tanuma Yoshinori|ja|田沼意明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanuma Yoshinori|qq=}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1796|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
